4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive 16-week course to become an AI Machine Learning Engineer, suitable for beginners. The program teaches essential skills in Python, SQL, Looker, and Statistics, enabling students to create predictive models and work with various machine learning algorithms. Participants will engage in real-life projects, mastering the full lifecycle of AI project development while ensuring data privacy and security.

Instruction is provided in small classes (max 12 students), with sessions conducted thrice a week. Graduates receive industry-recognized certificates. Courses are available in English and Spanish. 

